entries.journal_entry_description: I have been told to strike against the rebellion starting from the ground up. I will begin by attacking their elite forces. Then I will move up the chain of command and begin eliminating officers.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Destroy 5 Rebel Section Commanders in a contested city.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Kill 10 Elite Rebel Commandos in a contested city.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Eliminate 3 Rebel Corporals in a contested city.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Assassinate a Skilled Rebel Officer in a contested city.
